  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FRAG LIKE IT'S 1999</h2>TOXIKK™ plays as if today's military and MOBA shooters never existed: The game combines the simple and intuitive mechanics of old-school FPS giants with a fresh setting, slick graphics and our vision to carefully evolve the genre with some new ideas elaborated with Arena-FPS enthusiasts.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRY TOXIKK™ FOR FREE</h2><br>Note that the Free Edition does <strong>NOT HAVE ANY COMPETITIVE DISADVANTAGES</strong> versus the Full Game and is NOT some micro-transaction fueled <i>F2P</i> crap, but simply a classic shareware version / demo of the full game. If you decide to buy the Full Game, you <i>really</i> get the FULL game (i.e. ALL customizations and ALL features).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/324810/extras/266198dd15b94af5a8958bc779ae31e7.avif?t=1644043937\" width=600 height=816 /></span><br><br>* ALL MAPS CAN BE UNLOCKED THROUGH XP<br>** LIMITED TO MULTIPLAYER ACHIEVEMENTS<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >QUESTIONS?</h2><br>Meet the community on our Discord live Chat:<br>",
